                </h2>
                <hr class="thin">
                
                <div class="feed-item-listing span-19">   
                    <div class ="feed-item-listing-row">
                        <div class = "feed-item-listing-row-details span-19">
                             
                                <p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://media.rhizome.org/blog/9238/LDN.jpg" alt="" width="590" /></p>
<p>General admission tickets to the <a href="http://rhizome.org/sevenonseven">5th Anniversary edition</a> of Rhizome's Seven on Seven program, returning to the New Museum on May 3, are sold out. Missed your chance to buy tickets? Live somewhere other than New York City? Worry not—you can still join this celebration of art and tech. Details after the break. </p>
                                    
